snippet.title: Tanks Meet Zombies Trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/743340/Tanks_Meet_Zombies/

Dress up as an Assault Armored Vehicle and prepare yourself to speed date, we mean destroy, hordes and hordes of undying humans, bears, spiders and more! Join with up to 3 more friends and get ready to wreak havoc, it will be a BLAST!

Tanks Meet Zombies uses Merry Go Slower.

Merry Go Slower by Kevin MacLeod is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution license (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
Source: http://incompetech.com/music/royalty-free/index.html?isrc=USUAN1100732
Artist: http://incompetech.com/
